The paper discusses a competition of constraint solvers, which is a topic related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and data structures (cs.DS). The use of constraints in solving problems also relates to programming languages (cs.PL) and logic (cs.LO). Finally, the competition involves evaluating the performance of different solvers, which is a topic related to data mining (cs.DM).
